title: Jon Secada - Jon Secada (Flac) [FrankFoo]
description:
Jon Secada - Jon Secada (flac)

Jon Secada knows he has a great voice,and he shows it off on everyone 
of these 12 cuts.

Sometimes its a little too much.
My favorite cut is "Angel." 
I could listen to this song forever and never get tired of it."Dreams that I carry," the second number, really shows off this great talented singer.

You think he's done holding the note,but he goes higher,lower.
THIS GUY CAN SING.The other hit singles,"I'm Free,Just Another Day,Do You Believe in us," are all fantastic records.

I love his voice because the passion he feels for his music comes across to the listener. 
I just get caught up in the words and powerful meaning to his songs, especially I'm Free. 
That song paints a beautiful visual image (if you have an imagination) and empowers you.

If you love hearing a great male singer, Jon Secada's debut CD is a must have for your record collection.

Linage: CD > EAC > flac
